# License

In order to better support reuse of this software,

such as for [emanote-template](https://github.com/srid/emanote-template) and other uses,

the following paths within this directory:

- [`index.yaml`](index.yaml)
- [`templates/`](templates) (and all files within)

are licensed `SPDX-License-Identifier: CC0-1.0 OR AGPL-3.0-or-later`:

- [CC0 LICENSE]([LICENSE])
- [AGPL3 LICENSE](../LICENSE)

This means that you can choose to use the specified files under either of the licenses.

The files under [`lua-filters/`](lua-filters/) are MIT-licensed filters:
[`list-table.lua`](lua-filters/list-table.lua) is bundled from
[`pandoc-ext/list-table`](https://github.com/pandoc-ext/list-table), and
[`wordcount.lua`](lua-filters/wordcount.lua) is an Emanote-specific filter
derived from the retired
[`pandoc/lua-filters`](https://github.com/pandoc/lua-filters) wordcount
filter. See [`lua-filters/LICENSE`](lua-filters/LICENSE) for the bundled
license notices.
